item.title: [317] Need Runserver Help
item.dc:creator: @dannydude8 dannydude8
item.description:
@dannydude8 wrote:

[quote=“Coder Fatality, post:1, topic:348015”]I need help with the Runserver, Is java 20 the max java thing you can use? i have it, but i need a Runserver for java 20.
Anyone? i looked it on google and ask.com and on moparisthebest.com.[/quote]
You mean you need a compiler, here

[code]
@echo off
@TITLE EvolutionX
if exist “%programfiles%\Java” (call :compile “%programfiles%\Java”) else (goto error)
:compile
for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe")
if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java)
if defined p (goto end)
:error
echo You do not have Java installed. Please download it at the site that is about to load.
:end
echo Finished!
pause
exit


This automatically detects your jdk version
